- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as sketches have been used in natural language processing and machine learning applications.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possibility as sketches have been used in distributed machine learning systems.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a less likely category, but still possible as sketches have been used in distributed data sets.
